{
  "stem": "3341.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would establish a small textile school in, in the, under the auspices of the textile mill in Ruzomberok, which was one of the leading one.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they employed so many young people, which are like apprentices.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we could start the school with the apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, they would be trained to do a better work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And possibly later on, that can develop in a textile school, which happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the textile school is existing in Slovakia, even now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was such fantasy, which I, when I think about it today, I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had the chutzpah to, to write-- my older brother, of course, helped me, what, to put it together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I send the letter to the Ministry of Education in '43.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine what it means?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a fascistic government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't get any reply.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two weeks, three weeks, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then finally, I got a letter with the headline of Ministry of Education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I opened the letter and there was only two lines written, signed by Minister of Education. 'We received your letter and we would like to have a personal interview with you.' You know, I, I thought, I, I can't believe my eyes when it was happening.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to the interview.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to my luck-- everything in life depends, very many times, on your luck, how lucky you are or how game you are.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That Minister of Education was my professor from my gymnasium years, which were not many.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the history professor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A very good man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A very intelligent fellow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was actually a survivor from the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was Russian by background.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was, I think, taken prisoner in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
